title: Westward the Women (1951).avi
description:
Classic Western - Black and White

In a time when "The West" pretty much ends in Texas and only California is slowly being populated by the white men, there&#039;s a severe lack of women among the workers on Roy Whitman&#039;s farm in the California Valley. So he goes back east to Chicago to recruit wives for his employees. From the candidates he selects 150, who seem able to survive a months long journey across "The Great American Desert" and the Rocky Mountains.

This is not available in DVD remaster yet.  This is a VHS rip.  It is however, good quality and when I go full screen for the playback, the detail remains quite good.  Only one source on the entire eDonkey network.
